# Project Framework
- Package manager: pnpm
- This is an ESM module which uses uses the ".ts" extension for imports
- This project uses SolidJS, not React
- Use SolidJS syntax (e.g. class instead of className, createSignal instead of useState)
- Use solid-app-router for routing instead of react-router-dom
- Use CSS modules for styles

# Development Guidelines
- Prefer a functional style. Classes are almost never necessary – avoid them when possible, and NEVER use inheritance.

# Database Access
- SQLite database is stored in OPFS
- Use kysely for database operations
- Database schema is defined in [schemas.ts](mdc:front-end/src/types/schemas.ts)
